1020
01:25:35,467 --> 01:25:36,634
Thank you.

1021
01:26:13,634 --> 01:26:14,267
MacGyver!

1022
01:26:37,167 --> 01:26:38,400
Warning.

1023
01:26:38,400 --> 01:26:40,234
Uranium separator
failure imminent.

1024
01:26:40,234 --> 01:26:41,567
No! Stop!

1025
01:26:41,567 --> 01:26:43,267
I hate you!

1026
01:26:43,267 --> 01:26:44,367
Give it up!

1027
01:26:44,367 --> 01:26:46,133
Nuclear systems jeopardized.

1028
01:26:48,434 --> 01:26:50,667
Automatic override engaged.

1029
01:26:50,667 --> 01:26:52,634
Nuclear emergency averted.

1030
01:26:55,334 --> 01:26:59,367
Automatic override
has been bypassed.

1031
01:26:59,367 --> 01:27:01,200
System failure imminent.

1032
01:27:01,200 --> 01:27:03,567
All nuclear systems at risk.

1033
01:27:03,567 --> 01:27:05,434
Repeat:

1034
01:27:05,434 --> 01:27:08,033
system failure imminent.

1035
01:27:08,033 --> 01:27:10,400
All nuclear systems at risk.

1036
01:27:14,701 --> 01:27:15,767
Ah!

1037
01:27:18,000 --> 01:27:22,033
Nuclear systems operating
beyond design limits.

1038
01:27:22,033 --> 01:27:23,467
Red alert.

1039
01:27:23,467 --> 01:27:25,901
Plant failure imminent.

1040
01:27:25,901 --> 01:27:27,300
Repeat.

1041
01:27:27,300 --> 01:27:31,167
Nuclear systems operating
beyond design limits.

1042
01:27:31,167 --> 01:27:33,501
Red alert.
Plant failure imminent.

1043
01:27:46,734 --> 01:27:49,133
What have you done?
I've armed the bomb.

1044
01:27:49,133 --> 01:27:51,767
It can't be disarmed
without a trivet wrench.

1045
01:27:51,767 --> 01:27:53,934
You lose, MacGyver.

1046
01:27:53,934 --> 01:27:55,267
Now we all die.

1047
01:27:59,100 --> 01:28:03,434
Nuclear detonation
in one minute, 30 seconds.

1048
01:28:09,434 --> 01:28:12,868
Nuclear systems operating
beyond design limits.

1049
01:28:12,868 --> 01:28:14,467
Red alert.

1050
01:28:14,467 --> 01:28:16,901
Plant failure imminent.

1051
01:28:16,901 --> 01:28:18,033
Repeat.

1052
01:28:18,033 --> 01:28:20,200
Nuclear systems operating

1053
01:28:20,200 --> 01:28:22,133
beyond design limits.

1054
01:28:22,133 --> 01:28:24,634
Red alert.
Plant failure imminent.

1055
01:28:29,300 --> 01:28:31,901
Nuclear detonation
in one minute.

1056
01:28:40,033 --> 01:28:43,868
Detonation in 50 seconds.

1057
01:28:50,067 --> 01:28:53,701
Detonation in 40 seconds.

1058
01:28:53,701 --> 01:28:56,367
Uranium separators destroyed.

1059
01:28:56,367 --> 01:28:58,601
Nuclear facility is inoperative.

1060
01:28:58,601 --> 01:29:01,834
Detonation in 30 seconds.

1061
01:29:04,367 --> 01:29:07,200
Detonation in 25 seconds.

1062
01:29:10,667 --> 01:29:13,501
Detonation in 20 seconds.

1063
01:29:15,367 --> 01:29:17,901
Detonation in 15 seconds.

1064
01:29:19,100 --> 01:29:22,300
Detonation in ten seconds.

1065
01:29:22,300 --> 01:29:25,634
Nine, eight, seven,

1066
01:29:25,634 --> 01:29:28,534
six, five, four,

1067
01:29:28,534 --> 01:29:30,534
three, two...

1068
01:29:32,234 --> 01:29:35,300
Nuclear detonation averted.

1069
01:29:35,300 --> 01:29:38,033
Nuclear device disarmed.

1070
01:29:53,801 --> 01:29:55,334
You never give up, do you?

1071
01:29:56,767 --> 01:29:58,767
I guess it just wasn't
meant to be.

1072
01:30:10,534 --> 01:30:12,968
I owe you an apology, MacGyver.

1073
01:30:12,968 --> 01:30:15,367
We are on the same side.

1074
01:30:15,367 --> 01:30:16,400
Thanks for your help.

1075
01:30:18,167 --> 01:30:19,334
You bet, chief.

1076
01:30:19,334 --> 01:30:21,400
See you soon.
I hope.

1077
01:30:43,400 --> 01:30:45,534
My father cared
so much for this planet.

1078
01:30:45,534 --> 01:30:47,968
He just wanted to do some good.

1079
01:30:47,968 --> 01:30:49,567
He did.

1080
01:30:49,567 --> 01:30:51,634
The world's a safer place
because of Paul.

1081
01:30:51,634 --> 01:30:53,300
Maybe.

1082
01:30:53,300 --> 01:30:54,400
But my father,

1083
01:30:54,400 --> 01:30:55,734
your friend, he's gone.

1084
01:30:57,968 --> 01:31:00,534
Then I guess it's up to us.

